description:
This saddens me on so many levels!!🖤 I am Vegan and this affects me more so than if i still ate meat! These animals are being murdered in vein! Not to even be eaten just slaughtered & destroyed with no remorse by the government! They are also targeting dairy and vegetables! Now with that said, remember I told you guys to stock up on seeds and start growing your own! We are gonna see food shortages and no amount of money will change that! Rich & poor will be standing in lines waiting on government provisions which may or may not allotted without a Covid test or medical certification! Will you get a vaccine so you and your family can eat? 🚫💉
